    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nFor ui2, pressing `<CR>` right after a message will open the pager (like `g<`). However, this only works if `<CR>` is unbound. If a keymap is made, this functionality breaks.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nThe default behavior is what I would expect. However, it would be great to have an easy way of creating a keymap for `<CR>` while also keeping the special behavior.",
